Description: REOPENING THE R.F.K. INVESTIGATION / Paul Schrade and Allard Lowenstein| interviewed by Jim Berland. - Paul Schrade and Allard Lowenstein discuss the 1968 assassination of Presidential Candidate Robert F. Kennedy in Los Angeles, particularly focusing upon the need to reopen the case to uncover the real events. BROADCAST: KPFK, 13 Jan. 1973.
